body:
In League players only get 3 refunds for their entire accounts life. In my opinion I think it would be a really great idea if every time a new season starts players that have used all of their refunds get a refund token in their account but it is only used on what you bought in that season. I think it would be great to add into the client and it would keep players happy. I hope this feature can be thought about and added in the future as it would be really cool to see.
But it is only just a thought.
